Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.75,0:01:46.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why was I beaten?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.46,0:01:57.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I won't lose to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:01.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.50,0:02:07.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did I err somewhere?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.55,0:02:15.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, I've made no mistakes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.58,0:02:21.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as I have\nthis Sacred Jewel...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.95,0:02:24.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will be able to start\nover and over again!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:02:25.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.46,0:02:29.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.49,0:02:30.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you are human, be gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.86,0:02:32.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you are a demon,\nwe will slay you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.16,0:02:34.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stand back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:37.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am Priestess Tsubaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.74,0:02:40.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,At one time, I trained at\nthis shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.18,0:02:53.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.45,0:02:56.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nothing has changed much\nsince those days.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:02:59.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My name is Momiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.39,0:03:01.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am Botan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:04.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Only you two protect\nthis shrine now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.93,0:03:08.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We were Master's\nlast disciples.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:09.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.30,0:03:14.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Priestess Tsubaki, you said you\nwere Master's disciple, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.71,0:03:17.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please pardon my rudeness,\nbut how old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.94,0:03:20.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You look so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:23.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am much older than you,\nof course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.85,0:03:25.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But this is a result of my training.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:28.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is there a skill to keep\none young?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.15,0:03:32.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you continue your training,\nit will become possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:36.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not easy, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.46,0:03:42.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Priestess Tsubaki, why did you\nreturn to this shrine?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.07,0:03:45.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am being pursued by\na demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:45.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:46.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.57,0:03:49.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now then, what shall I do\nwith these two?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:51.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kill them off immediately?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.81,0:03:53.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We will assist, Priestess Tsubaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.11,0:03:56.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You are our sister disciple!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:03:58.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.29,0:04:07.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.83,0:04:08.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}After that time...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.90,0:04:13.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was under a curse placed\nby the Dark Priestess Tsubaki.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.84,0:04:26.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:28.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Feel all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.25,0:04:30.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:32.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.49,0:04:34.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.82,0:04:35.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:36.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.06,0:04:39.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look! I'm all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.46,0:04:43.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The sorceress who placed the\ncurse is named Tsubaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.23,0:04:50.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fifty years ago, she was a priestess\nequal in status to my sister, Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.64,0:04:52.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why did she turn into\nan evil priestess?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:54.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I do not know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.71,0:04:57.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Perhaps, the name is just\na coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.58,0:04:59.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.94,0:05:01.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I sense the presence of\nthe Sacred Jewel Shard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:04.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you sure, Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:06.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, I feel it very distinctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.48,0:05:08.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was a huge Shard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:10.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And? Which way is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.49,0:05:14.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.93,0:05:16.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We have no choice but to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.73,0:05:19.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, in order to get the\NSacred Jewel back,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.26,0:05:20.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,we must not miss\nthis opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.53,0:05:24.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What, Kaede?!\NYou mean to follow us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.64,0:05:26.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The enemy is\na Dark Shrine Maiden!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.10,0:05:29.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't it better if I, a shrine maiden,\ncame along?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.57,0:05:32.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you a shrine MAIDEN\neven when you're old?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.58,0:05:33.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.78,0:05:35.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.28,0:05:36.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Arghh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.05,0:05:38.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Impudent fellow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.42,0:05:40.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let us go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.35,0:05:42.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go, Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.69,0:05:44.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.19,0:05:46.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.63,0:05:48.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.06,0:05:49.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:52.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.73,0:05:54.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't forget me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:06.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You learn quickly, Tsubaki.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.64,0:06:08.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Really, Master?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.81,0:06:09.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.79,0:06:17.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Humph! Sixty years have passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:21.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's only natural that\nmy teacher is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.23,0:06:23.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Priestess Tsubaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.20,0:06:29.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Special charms unique to this shrine\nwould keep out any demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.30,0:06:31.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where could they be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:34.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please leave that to us,\NPriestess Tsubaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:38.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even if we cannot slay them,\nwe can at least hamper them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.48,0:06:39.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.88,0:06:42.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The enemy is a terrible,\nevil demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.58,0:06:47.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- We have trained hard and long, too.\N- It is our duty to fight demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.79,0:06:51.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then I shall leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:53.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Give me as much time\nas possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.79,0:06:54.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.37,0:07:02.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How's this, Momiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.87,0:07:05.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I think this will do fine, Botan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:08.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's our first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:10.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All the more reason for\njust doing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.38,0:07:14.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes! It's all part of\ntraining and experience, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:17.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Onward!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.32,0:07:19.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To slay the demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.80,0:07:42.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You must never open\nthese doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:44.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is the forbidden Pagoda\nof Many Treasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:51.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Forbidden, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.92,0:07:58.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.02,0:08:01.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku wants\nthe Sacred Jewel back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.26,0:08:03.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This belongs to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:09.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Didn't he promise to give it to you,\nonly IF you fulfilled his wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.03,0:08:13.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will fulfill his wish!\NBy using this Sacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.01,0:08:16.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That Kagome... and Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.11,0:08:17.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll kill them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:20.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How? You lost to them\nonce already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:24.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There is power here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:28.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Power that I can harvest with\nthis Sacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.02,0:08:31.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Doesn't sound very hopeful at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.46,0:08:34.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shall I tell you something\nvery interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.29,0:08:34.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.63,0:08:38.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The ultimate way to use\nthe Sacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.53,0:08:40.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.77,0:08:46.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.37,0:08:50.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Kirara?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.11,0:08:51.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:00.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.59,0:09:02.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.96,0:09:08.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A barrier we put up to prevent\ndemons from entering.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.29,0:09:10.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is it Tsubaki's doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.10,0:09:12.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I sense the Sacred Jewel\nbeyond this barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.30,0:09:16.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! I'll tear apart\nthis stupid barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.10,0:09:22.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oww! What IS this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:24.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.11,0:09:30.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, this isn't the time\nto be playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.62,0:09:33.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a barrier against demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:37.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just leave the barrier to\NKaede and myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.92,0:09:38.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.96,0:09:39.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you appeared, Demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.63,0:09:41.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We have been waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.43,0:09:43.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you Inuyasha,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.59,0:09:46.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the demon who seeks to\ndestroy Priestess Tsubaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:47.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.97,0:09:49.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you Tsubaki's cronies?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.03,0:09:51.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Priestess Tsubaki is\na sister disciple!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.17,0:09:53.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's only natural to\nbe her ally!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.27,0:09:57.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you're Dark Priestesses, too?\NI won't spare you either, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.64,0:09:58.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,D-Dark Priestesses?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:00.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How dare you insult us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.18,0:10:02.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you aren't Dark Priestesses?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.68,0:10:03.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous, Demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.95,0:10:06.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am Momiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:08.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I am Botan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.45,0:10:11.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We are priestesses\nwho have trained hard
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.62,0:10:12.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,in the art of slaying demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.02,0:10:15.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do not even mention us in the same\nbreath as the Dark Priestess!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.89,0:10:17.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They seem to be on\nthe side of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.66,0:10:21.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aren't they Tsubaki's helpers?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.87,0:10:24.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now, now you two.\NJust wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:25.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:27.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,From your appearance,\nyou seem to be a monk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.47,0:10:29.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And you are demon slayer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.68,0:10:31.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.28,0:10:36.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Look at those strange clothes!\N- But she seems to have power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.18,0:10:39.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You must be a priestess!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.98,0:10:41.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, I guess you could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.65,0:10:45.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So why do you side with\nsuch demons?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.62,0:10:47.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You think I'm a demon, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.19,0:10:50.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We haven't done anyone\nany harm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.83,0:10:51.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.53,0:10:52.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.80,0:10:55.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, Momiji...\nisn't he so cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.33,0:10:58.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh... cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:02.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And so is that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.41,0:11:04.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What'll we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.18,0:11:06.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What'll we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.08,0:11:10.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What'll we do?\NThey don't seem to be bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.38,0:11:13.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We have to\nconvince them somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.99,0:11:15.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hello there, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.49,0:11:16.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.32,0:11:19.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demon! You've disguised\nyour appearance!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.13,0:11:28.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,By changing\nyour disgusting looks,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:30.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you may have deceived\nthe rest of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.84,0:11:32.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But not us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.70,0:11:34.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We will not be fooled\nby what we see!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:39.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is it... Is it my fault?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.84,0:11:41.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop acting so scared, Shippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.65,0:11:44.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If they insist on interfering,\nwe have to use force!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.78,0:11:46.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:48.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's try talking to them\nsome more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.49,0:11:50.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go, Botan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.62,0:11:52.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Leave it to me, Momiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:54.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.46,0:11:57.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.46,0:11:59.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Why you!\N- When'd you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.77,0:12:05.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will explain why we're with\nthose demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.74,0:12:09.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It all started with the existence\nof the Sacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.51,0:12:12.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The demons coveted its power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.85,0:12:17.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:19.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You've sold your soul to\nthe demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.52,0:12:23.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My hand... My hand is possessed\nby the demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.42,0:12:26.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're possessed by something else!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.16,0:12:30.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you thinking?!\NGoing off course like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.83,0:12:32.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Err... sorry about that.\nl just...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.90,0:12:35.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is Tsubaki over yonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.53,0:12:36.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We will not let you pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.04,0:12:38.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.39,0:12:55.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.72,0:12:56.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Paper spirits, {\i1}Shikikami.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.82,0:12:57.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a spell in which...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.89,0:13:00.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,paper dolls are given souls\nwhich they control.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.13,0:13:07.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're very weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.07,0:13:10.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We can't take them\nseriously, can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.80,0:13:12.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.64,0:13:19.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're not bad, all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.45,0:13:23.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That was just a red herring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.48,0:13:27.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In order to get strands\nof your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.35,0:13:30.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?! They didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.02,0:13:32.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it, Kaede?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.09,0:13:35.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You intend to transfer our bodies\ninto those {\i1}Shikikami.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:37.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Very clever, Demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.80,0:13:39.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am a priestess!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.37,0:13:52.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Transfer our bodies?\NBut whose?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:53.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.95,0:13:56.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whoever it is,\NI'll smash them apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.58,0:14:01.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.62,0:14:02.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.05,0:14:04.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I think it can.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:06.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.19,0:14:08.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.26,0:14:11.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-Then... is... that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.36,0:14:13.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:14.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.27,0:14:16.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.53,0:14:18.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't that you, Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:26.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No! I don't look like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.29,0:14:45.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pretty elaborate ceremony, huh?\NIs the seal that strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.00,0:14:48.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This one is to open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.37,0:14:51.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There are even stronger\nseals further in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:02.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Botan, we did good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.98,0:15:05.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And they look cute, Momiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.02,0:15:07.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well? Are you shocked?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:10.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not only shape and form.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.29,0:15:13.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even the power has been\ntransferred totally intact!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:14.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It doesn't look like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:15.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's nothing like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.43,0:15:16.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.56,0:15:21.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Blasted tricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.63,0:15:25.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iron-reaver, Soul-stealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.87,0:15:27.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iron-reaver... Soul-stealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.15,0:15:37.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't get in the way, Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:40.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop calling that THING my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.09,0:15:42.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.66,0:15:47.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know! If that Shikikami\nis supposed to be Inuyasha...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.99,0:15:48.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.77,0:15:58.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!\NWhat're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:15:59.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:04.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not all of the powers of the host\nseems to be transferable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.34,0:16:06.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's still just a fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.18,0:16:08.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Although, I'm a bit jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.05,0:16:14.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's with that sword?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.39,0:16:16.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.73,0:16:23.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.66,0:16:25.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do something\nabout that Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.20,0:16:28.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't call it my name, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.60,0:16:31.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And why don't YOU do something\nabout that Inuyasha!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.47,0:16:32.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That ain't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.47,0:16:35.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh dear,\NI guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.04,0:16:37.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.41,0:16:39.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.41,0:16:44.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I feel a bit hesitant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.68,0:16:47.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku, can you take care\nof"Kagome"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.55,0:16:49.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't call it Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.49,0:16:52.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, I'll take care of"Inuyasha."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.72,0:16:54.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.23,0:16:57.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can fight "Inuyasha"\nwithout reservations.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:17:00.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What does that mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.13,0:17:02.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.13,0:17:04.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Move! You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.37,0:17:08.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll get rid of them with\nmy Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.15,0:17:16.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,On guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.05,0:17:23.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,M-My body!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.09,0:17:25.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, Demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.32,0:17:27.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll seal your movements!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:31.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.40,0:17:35.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh no! That cute little one\nis in pain, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.73,0:17:37.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.\NIt's a demon, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.27,0:17:40.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Enough, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.67,0:17:42.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That demon is still moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.37,0:17:44.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.31,0:17:45.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.38,0:17:52.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you get in our way,\nwe'll get rid of you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.45,0:17:56.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Stop already!\NWe haven't done anything bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.25,0:18:00.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Monk, let us subdue those\ntwo maidens first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,0:18:02.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess we have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.73,0:18:06.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do not interfere with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.76,0:18:11.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you!\NEnough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.07,0:18:18.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you don't cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.95,0:18:25.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stubborn demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:26.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We won't lose either!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.22,0:18:27.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.92,0:18:28.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.73,0:18:36.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm free!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.43,0:18:41.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.04,0:18:54.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.28,0:19:02.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.99,0:19:08.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.76,0:19:15.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They've just fainted.\NTheir lives aren't in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.37,0:19:20.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And they don't seem to be hurt...\NOwwee!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.64,0:19:23.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What'll we do with these two?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.07,0:19:27.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When they come to, will they\nattack us again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.68,0:19:29.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tsubaki tricked them or\nsweet-talked them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.45,0:19:33.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In any case, I think they'd understand\nif we explain it thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.45,0:19:37.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And who's gonna take on\nsuch a silly task!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.35,0:19:39.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naturally, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.19,0:19:39.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.42,0:19:43.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will take them both in\nand explain in detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.46,0:19:47.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo, will you stay\nwith Miroku?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.50,0:19:50.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Me?\NBut what am I to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.73,0:19:53.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All you have to do is keep\nan eye on Miroku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.47,0:19:58.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Besides, it'll be easy for you\nto convince them...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.54,0:19:59.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,that you're not a bad demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.44,0:20:01.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I must be strong and alert!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.98,0:20:03.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara, you stay, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.05,0:20:07.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do as you please!\NI'm going after Tsubaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.19,0:20:09.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.86,0:20:16.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait until I bring down\nthe barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.50,0:20:21.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It will open soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.67,0:20:24.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just what's inside there anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.97,0:20:26.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.31,0:20:33.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}100 years ago, the head priest\nlost many of his men...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.01,0:20:36.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and it was all he could do to\nseal it in the Pagoda...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.45,0:20:37.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This demon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.92,0:20:39.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's such a frightening\ndemon inside?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:43.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Generation after generation has taken turns\nmaking sure the door remained sealed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.65,0:20:47.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tsubaki, in time, you will be\ngiven this duty.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.29,0:20:49.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, Master!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.23,0:20:53.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You must never open it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:55.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It is the forbidden Pagoda!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.21,0:21:09.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The demon sealed inside this\nforbidden Pagoda is enormously strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.18,0:21:10.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.75,0:21:14.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You intend to use the Sacred Jewel\nto make him heed your orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.19,0:21:17.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes. I'll use it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.56,0:21:20.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't intend it all to end yet!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.70,0:21:26.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can see something!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.13,0:21:29.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I feel the Sacred Jewel just ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.67,0:21:31.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is Tsubaki there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.84,0:21:40.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.74,0:21:41.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.95,0:21:44.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even the gate has\na barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.66,0:21:54.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's so reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.03,0:21:57.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Come on out, Tsubaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.14,0:23:52.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why? Why did I lose to Kikyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.44,0:23:53.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is that Pagoda?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.81,0:23:55.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did Tsubaki escape into that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.15,0:23:58.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What am I lacking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.72,0:23:59.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's Kagura!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.22,0:24:02.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So Naraku and Tsubaki are\nin cahoots, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.99,0:24:03.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.12,0:24:06.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you desire the Sacred Jewel,\nyou must obey me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.56,0:24:11.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"The Forbidden Pagoda and the Giant Demon!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.46,0:24:14.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will attain eternity!
